<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>ROCK STAR:</h1>
  <h2>Weapon of Choice</h2>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
      <p class="lead">No rock star worth their rhinestones ever hits the stage without brandishing their weapon of choice! Use this API to discover the arsenal of your favorite artists or find out who prefers any particular face-melting instrument.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2 col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-8">
      <h1 class="text-center">Try it out!</h1>
      <div class="input-group">
        <span class="input-group-addon">http://localhost:3000/api/</span>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="request-url-input" aria-describedby="basic-addon3" value="rock-stars">
        <span class="input-group-btn">
          <button id="request-btn" class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Request</button>
        </span>
      </div>
      <small>Try
        <a href="#" class="hint">
          <i>rock-stars/1</i>
        </a> or
        <a href="#" class="hint">
          <i>weapons/2</i>
        </a>
      </small>
      <h4>Response:</h4>
      <div class="well">
        <pre id="responseOutput" class="pre-scrollable">
        </pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2 col-md-2"></div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1>How to Use</h1>
        </div>
        <p>There are two endpoints with accessible data, <code>/rock-stars</code> and <code>/weapons</code>. Use our RESTful API to gather data from each resource or search by ID to grab the associations: <code>/weapons/2</code>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1>Posting to the Database</h1>
        </div>
        <p>
          Who wants to see their rock 'n roll idols that have forgotten to bring their rigs to the gig? <strong>Nobody.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          What good is a guitar if no one ever plays it? <strong>It's not.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          In order to post to this database you will need to include at least one artist and one of their weapons of choice so neither will feel useless!
        </p>
        <p>Send a <code>POST</code> request to the <code>api/star-weapon</code> endpoint, making sure to include the right data package, or just use our handy form!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3"></div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <form class="post-form">
    <div id="request-success" class="alert alert-success text-center hidden">
      <strong>Success!</strong> Your POST was made successfully!
    </div>
    <div id="request-fail" class="alert alert-danger text-center hidden">
      <strong>Oh no!</strong> Your POST was unsuccessful!
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-1 col-lg-1 col-md-1"></div>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-lg-5 col-md-5">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3>Rock Star</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="rock-star-name">Name</label>
          <input name="name" type="text" class="form-control" id="rock-star-name" placeholder="Rock Star name" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="rock-star-image">Image link</label>
          <input name="rockstarImg" type="text" class="form-control" id="rock-star-image" placeholder="Image link">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-lg-5 col-md-5">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3>Weapon of Choice</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="weapon-make">Make</label>
          <input name="make" type="text" class="form-control" id="weapon-make" placeholder="Make" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="weapon-model">Model</label>
          <input name="model" type="text" class="form-control" id="weapon-model" placeholder="Model" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="weapon-image">Image link</label>
          <input name="weaponImg" type="text" class="form-control" id="weapon-image" placeholder="Image link">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-1 col-lg-1 col-md-1"></div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="text-center">
      <button type="submit" class="post-form-submit btn-lg btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
